item.dc:creator: shanteau64
item.content:encoded:
This opportunity is like no other. We offer exceptional services with the gadget to do so. You don't want to miss out on this.

Virtual Open House

An open house is the tour of the property you're interested in. Many other people who are interested will also be there touring. Which is where our offer of the Virtual open house comes in......ONLY $40000.00 with the FREE gadget to do so.

Learn more

Virtual Reality Headsets that shows Blueprint

This offer you cannot dismiss. We are offering 3D cameras which improves the visibility of the representation of the blueprint........ONLY $25000.00 with the FREE HEADSET

Learn more

Online Consultations

Do you really want to drive to an office building just for a 15 minutes meeting. With the online consultation all you have to do is send an email and we can have the meeting right then and there , in the comfort of your own space without the hassle...... it varies up to $5000.00

Learn more

My husband and i were trying to get a house for the longest ,and when i got pregnant i realized we needed to move faster before the baby comes. We had a lot of questions and he had demanding hours so it was hard to go back and forth, this was in my third trimester . I thanked God everyday that TRE's Agency offered online consultations it was a big help.

— Samantha Little-James

We travel a lot as a couple and we wanted a house so bad to just settle once we got married . But we were so far away from Jamaica. This offer of virtual open house was the best thing that ever happened to us. We sent them an email gave our current address and they sent the gadget to access the virtual open house . We truly do respect the TRE's Agency.

— Mary Paul & John Paul

item.title: Services we Offer
item.dc:creator: shanteau64
item.content:encoded:
Meet our top agent for the Month. This spectacular individual has been with us for 3 years and counting she has made the company over $12 million in just her first year.

HERE's WHAT MAKES US SPECIAL

Virtual Open House

As we know an open house is the tour of the property the client is interested in. What we have to offer is the virtual open house where you won't have to come in at all. it helps if you have social issues too , it helps if you're minimizing the face to face contact with strangers. The most you would have to do is send an email. Once you send the email with the offer you are interested i.e Virtual Open House and your address we will send the gadget fit for that purpose and update you how to connect.

VR Headsets that shows Blueprint

If you are a skeptical and in depth person . This is the offer for you. We have this type of services for clients who want to know the dimension and the house or building layout , the type of wood , what bricks made it etc. You want to imagine yourself feeling it. This is an in person offer if you don't want the hard copy of the blueprint. Once again you just need to send an email with the requirements a gadget and a date will be sent for you in the reply.

Online Consultation

Online Consultation . We have this offer so it wouldn't be a hassle to drive from wherever to a short meeting just for a few queries. We have all the answers to your problems, enquiring about buying , enquiring about selling, advice on the type of home you want or the building you would like to start up your business just by sending an email. And don't worry we have an automated system so we would reply as soon as you send your request. All you have to do is send us an email with the query in the subject , your home address and we will take it from there.

item.title: About us
item.dc:creator: shanteau64
item.content:encoded:
TRE's Agency

Hello! This is TRE's Agency, in a world where everything is either on the phone or the internet . We created Techy's Real Estate, everything is online. We were a small agency during the years of 2015-2019 but as the days go by there was a demand for it especially in 2020 with COVID coming about. We're a young agency just living up to modernized times.

Vision Statement

Our vision is to be as transparent as our virtual reality headsets with our clients and our employees. Through building client and employee relationships with a level of professionalism , whatever our clients may need is what they will receive.

Mission Statement

To achieve , we are dedicated to creating an efficient and effective workplace . Being satisfied and apply which will increase production and once that energy is filled within the workplace it will expand to our clients.
